{"tid":2310372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《新香港》創刊號","createTime":"2020-12-03T08:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T23:26:16.000Z","uid":261647,"like":87,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6ffdefea6b1f67bec49a30f437a8904cbf5aef","tid":2310372,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/s/hkstandstrong_promo/59043\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2Fhkstandstrong_promo%2F59043&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=a09b31bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/hkstandstrong_promo/59043</a><br />\n<br />\n【《新香港》創刊號】<br />\n<br />\n《新香港》係一本政治理論刊物，刊出文章內容嘅主題環繞香港民族及香港民族主義等相關理論。<br />\n<br />\n另外，本刊將每期連載《香港志》及其譯本章節，原文以英文寫成，配以香港語譯文。《香港志》仿照羅馬時期作家塔斯佗嘅《日耳曼尼亞志》而創作，作者嘗試從「外來者」嘅視角描述香港民族各範疇，當中包括語言、生活習慣、信仰、居住地，藉此解構「何為香港民族」嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n第一期目錄：<br />\n香港民族及其祖地<br />\n三文兩語：確立新香港嘅語言主張<br />\n縱權而審 殃民之庭&mdash;&mdash;論香港法庭五宗罪<br />\nThe New Revolution<br />\n《香港志》連載（一）<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nIssuu: <a href=\"https://issuu.com/thenewhongkong/docs/thenewhongkong_vol1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fissuu.com%2Fthenewhongkong%2Fdocs%2Fthenewhongkong_vol1&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=ff84bf94\" target=\"_blank\">https://issuu.com/thenewhongkong/docs/thenewhongkong_vol1</a><br />\nGoogle Drive: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-DCKGdtKBGa0jOqKny4Yp6lYI4HW8y3l/view?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1-DCKGdtKBGa0jOqKny4Yp6lYI4HW8y3l%2Fview%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=b627067c\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-DCKGdtKBGa0jOqKny4Yp6lYI4HW8y3l/view?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn4.telesco.pe/file/RVB48qgbveTAOc81qg9CYmHtWZlcu-9uE5jJ5cjLsaauk4YhzRGLz7opTzyFioPPg--yKsVGrXdhsjaCdpIBJ113xeD_o9e9gNMMaS_eZwtybWvoS